A SERIES of new products, including jewellery, footware and homeware is being unveiled to launch a new drive. Made In Glasgow to be launched at Artstore A SERIES of new products, including jewellery, footware and homeware is being unveiled to launch a new drive.Made in Glasgow is aimed at generating and promoting new products from young city artists, designers and craft makers.The project is being run by Glasgow arts supplies company Artstore.There will be an opportunity to meet the creators of the first six products at the launch reception on October 2 at the Queen Street store.